00:42:04,600 --> 00:42:09,240
But you must do everything
I say without any exceptions.

482
00:42:10,680 --> 00:42:11,800
Okay?

483
00:42:12,400 --> 00:42:13,520
Okay.

484
00:42:20,600 --> 00:42:22,360
I’ll show you who’s the real prey.

485
00:42:36,800 --> 00:42:38,560
Hey, what are you doing?

486
00:42:41,880 --> 00:42:43,520
Why are you angry with me?

487
00:42:45,400 --> 00:42:46,480
I’m not.

488
00:42:48,920 --> 00:42:52,920
Rain, tell me.
I wanna know.

489
00:42:54,720 --> 00:42:57,680
You really don’t know why I’m angry?

490
00:43:00,360 --> 00:43:04,640
Then continue being in the dark.
I’ll stay angry, I’ll sulk.

491
00:43:05,800 --> 00:43:07,480
And I won’t talk to you.

492
00:43:12,000 --> 00:43:13,200
Tell me.

493
00:43:14,120 --> 00:43:20,480
What can I do to make
you naughty boy forgive me?

494
00:43:27,840 --> 00:43:31,960
Well, you must do as I say.

495
00:43:33,480 --> 00:43:35,080
What do you want me to do?

496
00:43:40,800 --> 00:43:41,800
Just a sec.

497
00:43:51,160 --> 00:43:52,760
You said you’d do it for me.

498
00:43:53,680 --> 00:43:57,720
Think of it as a way
to fulfil your promise.

499
00:44:08,080 --> 00:44:10,680
Why did you bring me up here?

500
00:44:12,360 --> 00:44:14,920
Didn’t you say you’d do
everything as I say?

501
00:44:17,120 --> 00:44:23,520
I can do everything you want me to.
But I’m just curious.

502
00:44:25,800 --> 00:44:29,560
Rule No. 1: You don’t have to do anything.

503
00:44:30,000 --> 00:44:31,040
Huh?

504
00:44:32,760 --> 00:44:37,520
Rule No. 2: You must
not respond to whatever I do.

505
00:44:37,680 --> 00:44:38,680
Huh?

506
00:44:39,600 --> 00:44:44,080
And rule No. 3: If you can’t
follow the first two rules...

507
00:44:44,880 --> 00:44:48,360
I won’t forgive you and
tell you why I’m angry.

508
00:44:50,200 --> 00:44:53,960
- Understood?
- Hold on a sec, I’m confused.

509
00:44:54,240 --> 00:44:57,760
How can I make up with you
if you won’t let me do anything?

510
00:45:02,720 --> 00:45:04,640
Wait, why are you taking off your clothes?

511
00:45:06,960 --> 00:45:07,960
P’ Pai.

512
00:45:13,800 --> 00:45:15,720
- Let’s take a bath.
- Huh?

513
00:45:25,880 --> 00:45:26,880
Okay.

514
00:45:28,320 --> 00:45:29,640
Let’s take a bath.

515
00:45:45,880 --> 00:45:48,040
- Will you forgive me now?
- No.

516
00:45:48,280 --> 00:45:50,200
Stand still.
I’m gonna take photos.

517
00:45:51,400 --> 00:45:56,200
Are you angry about the play’s costume?

518
00:45:56,320 --> 00:45:58,600
No.
Who’d be angry about such a silly matter?

519
00:45:59,120 --> 00:46:02,960
I’m angry that my boyfriend’s
annoyingly charming.

520
00:46:04,360 --> 00:46:12,080
Is it because I forced you to
read until you called me Daddy?

521
00:46:12,080 --> 00:46:14,120
No, it’s not about that.

522
00:46:15,120 --> 00:46:16,160
It’s not?

523
00:46:17,480 --> 00:46:21,320
Then it must be when
I punished you until you were sore.

524
00:46:21,760 --> 00:46:24,280
But I remember that you liked it.

525
00:46:25,400 --> 00:46:26,440
Not that!

526
00:46:26,560 --> 00:46:29,600
You brought a random woman home
and made out with her.

527
00:46:35,840 --> 00:46:39,440
When?
I never do that to anyone but you.

528
00:46:40,320 --> 00:46:41,520
Don’t you argue with me.

529
00:46:41,720 --> 00:46:45,800
She was beautiful, had nice body.
It’s still fresh in my memory.

530
00:46:45,840 --> 00:46:49,680
She was wearing an orange dress
and had this round thingy on her head.

531
00:46:53,560 --> 00:46:54,560
Ms. Natsu.

532
00:46:55,360 --> 00:46:56,400
Ms. Natsu?

533
00:46:57,360 --> 00:46:58,800
I don’t wanna know her name.

534
00:46:58,840 --> 00:47:02,360
But you’ve finally admitted that
you brought a woman home, right?

535
00:47:07,040 --> 00:47:09,720
That’s right, I brought a woman home.

536
00:47:10,640 --> 00:47:12,120
How could you do it, P’ Payu?

537
00:47:12,800 --> 00:47:14,480
How could you do this to me?

538
00:47:21,080 --> 00:47:25,520
But they’re just hotel
reservation documents.

539
00:47:26,800 --> 00:47:28,520
Why did you deliver them yourself?

540
00:47:35,400 --> 00:47:38,760
I’d like to ask you a favor, Mr. Payu.

541
00:47:39,280 --> 00:47:45,000
Since we’re in the same circle of friends,
I hope you won’t turn down my request.

542
00:47:48,240 --> 00:47:49,560
Is it about P’ Pakin?

543
00:47:52,760 --> 00:47:56,600
I’ve heard from my friends
that you’re close to Mr. Pakin.

544
00:47:56,880 --> 00:48:00,240
And he’s been planning
to expand his business.

545
00:48:00,640 --> 00:48:03,480
So I'm hoping that we can talk.

546
00:48:06,400 --> 00:48:08,200
I don’t think I can help you.

547
00:48:12,200 --> 00:48:17,720
How about an upgrade from a seaside
resort to a villa on a private island?

548
00:48:18,040 --> 00:48:19,480
What do you think?

549
00:48:20,480 --> 00:48:22,640
All you need to do is introduce me to him.

550
00:48:23,320 --> 00:48:26,680
It’s not easy to bribe me.

551
00:48:27,440 --> 00:48:29,200
It’s just an introduction.

552
00:48:35,960 --> 00:48:41,480
Mr. Pai told me you wanted to
take your important person on a trip.

553
00:48:42,320 --> 00:48:47,440
If you’re looking for surprise packages,
our affiliated hotels are at your service.

554
00:48:50,680 --> 00:48:53,840
- I’m not easily swayed.
- What about this time?

555
00:49:03,080 --> 00:49:04,840
Your offers hit the spot.

556
00:49:06,560 --> 00:49:09,600
- I’ll introduce you to him.
- Thank you.

557
00:49:10,360 --> 00:49:12,640
This person must be
very important to you.

558
00:49:14,720 --> 00:49:16,360
What do you think, Ms. Natsu?

559
00:49:19,520 --> 00:49:21,360
Your smile says it all.

560
00:49:21,360 --> 00:49:23,600
Don’t worry, I’ll rebook
for you immediately.

561
00:49:23,640 --> 00:49:28,000
And if you want to plan a surprise
event, I’ll take care of it for you.

562
00:49:28,760 --> 00:49:30,960
- Thank you.
- Thank you too.

563
00:49:35,600 --> 00:49:37,520
That woman’s my friend.

564
00:49:40,320 --> 00:49:41,600
I’m telling the truth.

565
00:49:41,640 --> 00:49:44,400
Pai can verify that we’re
in the same circle of friends.

566
00:49:45,320 --> 00:49:48,800
I asked her to help me book
a villa on a private island.

567
00:49:49,560 --> 00:49:53,240
‘Cause a certain boy wanted to go on
vacation before new semester started.

568
00:49:53,640 --> 00:49:55,600
But it seems he misunderstood.

569
00:49:57,440 --> 00:49:58,440
You’re lying.

570
00:50:00,040 --> 00:50:02,000
Have I ever lied to you about this stuff?

571
00:50:02,920 --> 00:50:07,560
I made a promise that
I'd never let you down.

572
00:50:13,080 --> 00:50:17,080
Umm… I guess I’m mistaken.

573
00:50:24,800 --> 00:50:28,800
That being said,
you promised to cosplay for me.

574
00:50:30,320 --> 00:50:33,280
Next outfit.
Go get changed now.

575
00:50:33,680 --> 00:50:37,880
- Must I get changed again?
- Yeah, hurry up and change your clothes.

576
00:50:42,280 --> 00:50:43,600
Shit.

577
00:50:45,320 --> 00:50:46,800
That was a huge misunderstanding.

578
00:50:47,200 --> 00:50:51,760
A villa reservation for our vacation?
Damn, I totally got the wrong idea.

579
00:50:54,360 --> 00:50:58,480
My boyfriend’s so great.
How did I misunderstand him?

580
00:51:01,960 --> 00:51:03,880
But the pilot outfit was so good.

581
00:51:11,960 --> 00:51:14,720
Hey, where’s the doctor uniform?

582
00:51:19,160 --> 00:51:20,920
I prefer it like this.

583
00:51:28,600 --> 00:51:34,320
Time to punish the boy who misunderstood
and made me run around looking for him.

584
00:51:36,240 --> 00:51:39,480
Who says you can punish me?
I’m still angry with you.

585
00:51:43,040 --> 00:51:45,280
I’m trying to make it up to you now.

586
00:52:04,520 --> 00:52:05,640
Let’s make up.

587
00:53:10,800 --> 00:53:12,280
What did I tell you?

588
00:53:12,480 --> 00:53:14,080
Aren’t you too mean?

589
00:53:14,440 --> 00:53:16,840
You expect me to do nothing
in this kind of situation?

590
00:53:17,720 --> 00:53:18,920
You’re killing me.

591
00:53:20,520 --> 00:53:23,160
You said you’d do anything.

592
00:53:23,720 --> 00:53:25,560
Can’t you do this much for me?

593
00:53:25,680 --> 00:53:28,800
Then how do you expect me
to believe your words?

594
00:53:30,040 --> 00:53:33,360
Sometimes I’ve got
a feeling that you’re mean.

595
00:53:35,000 --> 00:53:39,960
- So you’re gonna look for someone else?
- Hold on, I only love you.

596
00:53:46,800 --> 00:53:48,000
One foul.

597
00:53:48,600 --> 00:53:51,160
Get three fouls and
I’ll stop talking to you.

598
00:53:53,000 --> 00:53:54,840
I’m sorry, that was unintentional.

599
00:53:57,080 --> 00:53:59,240
You think I don’t know
that you did it on purpose?

600
00:54:03,760 --> 00:54:07,920
Rule No. 1: Prapai
won’t do anything to Sky.

601
00:54:08,600 --> 00:54:14,040
Rule No. 2: Prapai won’t
respond to whatever Sky does.

602
00:54:15,040 --> 00:54:21,760
Rule No. 3: If Prapai can’t follow
the first two rules, Sky won’t forgive him.

603
00:54:22,800 --> 00:54:23,800
Copy that!

604
00:54:25,840 --> 00:54:27,640
You’d better stick to the rules.

605
00:54:28,320 --> 00:54:30,520
Oh, did you just smile?

606
00:54:34,480 --> 00:54:36,200
Put your hands on the edge.

607
00:54:37,200 --> 00:54:38,200
The edge?

608
00:54:54,200 --> 00:54:58,600
Do you wanna know
the reason I’m angry with you?

609
00:55:16,680 --> 00:55:18,320
Then you need to endure.

610
00:55:23,960 --> 00:55:27,720
Don’t move, Pai.
Don’t move.

611
00:55:29,440 --> 00:55:30,680
Don’t move.

612
00:55:33,440 --> 00:55:37,800
Stay down, my son.
Stay down! Stay down!

613
00:55:38,240 --> 00:55:39,480
Stay the hell down!

614
00:55:42,080 --> 00:55:43,120
P’ Pai.

615
00:55:43,920 --> 00:55:45,760
- Hmm?
- Open your eyes.

616
00:55:46,320 --> 00:55:50,360
No, this isn’t the best
situation to open my eyes.

617
00:55:54,680 --> 00:55:56,600
I told you to open your eyes.

618
00:56:12,040 --> 00:56:13,480
Do you wanna kiss me?

619
00:56:15,040 --> 00:56:16,160
Absolutely.

620
00:56:21,800 --> 00:56:23,240
Then next time...

621
00:56:27,080 --> 00:56:29,520
Don’t let your ex pester me again.

622
00:56:34,800 --> 00:56:37,520
Remember the day we went on
a date and met your ex-girlfriend?

623
00:56:37,560 --> 00:56:39,000
She isn’t my ex-girlfriend.

624
00:56:42,320 --> 00:56:45,040
She said you’d never
be serious about anyone.

625
00:56:45,040 --> 00:56:48,000
But I’m serious about you.
Please believe me.

626
00:56:50,760 --> 00:56:51,800
I know that.

627
00:56:52,240 --> 00:56:53,240
Huh?

628
00:56:54,680 --> 00:56:57,280
I know she was trying to provoke me.

629
00:56:57,480 --> 00:57:00,280
And I know she was jealous
that you called me your boyfriend.

630
00:57:00,440 --> 00:57:03,640
And I also know that
she wanted my boyfriend.

631
00:57:06,160 --> 00:57:07,280
But...

632
00:57:07,440 --> 00:57:11,400
But I know better than anyone
that you’re not that kind of man.

633
00:57:13,120 --> 00:57:16,400
You’re serious about me.
You love me.

634
00:57:19,360 --> 00:57:21,520
But I still wanna get angry with you.

635
00:57:25,480 --> 00:57:26,720
I’m sorry.

636
00:57:27,480 --> 00:57:30,680
I promise I won’t let anything
like this happen again.

637
00:57:34,080 --> 00:57:39,280
And do you wanna know
what I wanna get angry about?

638
00:57:45,880 --> 00:57:50,880
I wanna get very angry that other
people saw a side of you I never saw.

639
00:57:52,160 --> 00:57:54,840
You’ve really got no idea how greedy I am.

640
00:57:55,560 --> 00:57:58,560
I wanna keep you to myself.
I don’t wanna share you with anyone else.

641
00:57:59,080 --> 00:58:01,280
I wish I could’ve been
the first person to touch you.

642
00:58:01,440 --> 00:58:02,480
And...

643
00:58:04,320 --> 00:58:05,600
I sound selfish.

644
00:58:08,160 --> 00:58:11,440
Not at all.
I feel that way too.

645
00:58:12,280 --> 00:58:16,200
Did you forget how much
I hate your ex-boyfriend?

646
00:58:21,200 --> 00:58:23,280
You’ve got a right to be angry with me.

647
00:58:24,480 --> 00:58:28,640
A right over my body, my heart.

648
00:58:31,400 --> 00:58:33,040
A right to my love.

649
00:58:35,480 --> 00:58:40,840
I’m sorry that my past
has made you feel upset.

650
00:58:43,040 --> 00:58:44,320
Are we good now?

651
00:58:52,040 --> 00:58:53,040
Ouch!

652
00:58:54,960 --> 00:58:59,240
Yes, we’re good now.
And that was the second foul.

653
00:58:59,280 --> 00:59:02,480
- Hey, did that count?
- Of course!

654
00:59:02,720 --> 00:59:06,960
We’ve made up, but I never
said your punishment was over.

655
00:59:07,680 --> 00:59:11,360
So don’t move.
Understood?

656
00:59:13,040 --> 00:59:14,080
Understood.

657
00:59:19,600 --> 00:59:23,680
Let’s see how long you can last.

658
00:59:29,120 --> 00:59:33,560
Just kill me.
Kill me, kill me right now!

659
00:59:34,840 --> 00:59:35,960
You little devil.

660
00:59:48,320 --> 00:59:50,040
You’re allowed to touch this much.

661
01:00:07,360 --> 01:00:08,440
Sky.

662
01:00:23,720 --> 01:00:27,840
You’re telling me that you knew
P’ Payu and P’ Pai would follow us here?

663
01:00:28,000 --> 01:00:29,080
Yeah.

664
01:00:30,280 --> 01:00:31,320
How did you know?

665
01:00:31,960 --> 01:00:35,680
I knew from the moment you sent
messages to Student Club’s chat group.

666
01:00:35,960 --> 01:00:38,680
Look, did you forget that
P’ Payu knows the club’s members?

667
01:00:38,880 --> 01:00:43,200
So I thought they might follow us here
but didn’t expect it to be so soon.

668
01:00:45,680 --> 01:00:49,040
So you told Rain to
come up with my punishment.

669
01:00:50,080 --> 01:00:53,320
I only asked him what he’d do
if you came here to apologize.

670
01:00:54,160 --> 01:00:56,440
And he prepared the rest himself.

671
01:00:57,280 --> 01:00:58,920
I didn't plan to use them here.

672
01:01:00,360 --> 01:01:06,560
I planned to punish P’ Payu if he came
to apologize after I returned to Bangkok.

673
01:01:07,600 --> 01:01:09,480
So I brought them with me.

674
01:01:10,120 --> 01:01:13,200
Wasn’t it because you
liked to see me cosplay?

675
01:01:13,960 --> 01:01:18,040
There are a pilot uniform,
a doctor uniform…

676
01:01:19,080 --> 01:01:21,120
Eat up, P' Payu.

677
01:01:25,440 --> 01:01:29,000
The dough sticks are very tasty.
So eat up.

678
01:01:29,040 --> 01:01:32,560
Is it tasty?
Let me feed you.

679
01:01:32,720 --> 01:01:34,200
You're really something, Rainy Boy.

680
01:01:34,680 --> 01:01:37,800
Be quiet, P’ Pai.
You were acting timid with Sky just now.

681
01:01:38,960 --> 01:01:40,440
He scolded me.

682
01:01:42,680 --> 01:01:43,920
Any other costumes you want?

683
01:01:46,080 --> 01:01:52,000
Eat up. Bite it, bite. Gobble it down.
Eat with this dip. It’s very sweet.

684
01:01:54,960 --> 01:01:56,520
- How about a racing suit?
- Open your mouth.

685
01:02:00,240 --> 01:02:03,280
It’s nice to go on
vacation once in a while.

686
01:02:05,040 --> 01:02:07,640
Let’s go on a trip next week.
Just the two of us.

687
01:02:13,000 --> 01:02:15,640
I’m talking about the villa on
a private island, naughty boy.

688
01:02:15,880 --> 01:02:18,640
I just told you yesterday.
Forget it already?

689
01:02:19,800 --> 01:02:21,200
You bullied me again.

690
01:02:22,920 --> 01:02:26,920
I didn’t forget.
But you’re really serious about it?

691
01:02:29,600 --> 01:02:33,200
It’s a reward for the good
boy who’s worked hard.

692
01:02:34,520 --> 01:02:38,760
Then I’ll study hard every year and
snatch the first-class honor for you.

693
01:02:40,360 --> 01:02:42,920
But I don’t think you can do it.

694
01:02:44,920 --> 01:02:46,200
P’ Payu.

695
01:02:47,800 --> 01:02:49,760
Can’t you just encourage me?

696
01:02:50,600 --> 01:02:52,400
I’m just being honest.

697
01:03:01,440 --> 01:03:04,920
I love you, P' Payu.

698
01:03:13,280 --> 01:03:16,160
P’ Pai and Sky are gonna see us.

699
01:03:17,600 --> 01:03:20,280
They won’t.
They’re over there.

700
01:03:27,280 --> 01:03:30,120
I’m leaving.
I don’t wanna stay with a bully.

701
01:03:30,920 --> 01:03:33,280
I’m gonna ask Sky to swim with me.

702
01:03:35,800 --> 01:03:36,800
Rain.

703
01:03:42,400 --> 01:03:43,960
I love you too.

704
01:03:58,960 --> 01:04:00,200
Do you like the sea?

705
01:04:01,440 --> 01:04:02,480
Yes.

706
01:04:04,120 --> 01:04:07,200
Then shall we have a beach wedding?

707
01:04:11,760 --> 01:04:16,240
You must’ve forgotten that same sex
marriage isn’t legalized in this country.

708
01:04:17,280 --> 01:04:20,200
But I believe there’ll be
changes in the future.

709
01:04:21,200 --> 01:04:24,600
‘Cause everyone’s got a right
to take care of people they love.

710
01:04:26,360 --> 01:04:28,520
And I wanna have that
right to take care of you.

711
01:04:33,560 --> 01:04:35,520
Are you asking me…

712
01:04:36,840 --> 01:04:37,920
To marry you?

713
01:04:39,440 --> 01:04:41,160
I can get serious at times too.

714
01:04:51,000 --> 01:04:54,280
Not today. Not now.

715
01:04:56,760 --> 01:04:59,240
Maybe after your graduation.

716
01:05:01,160 --> 01:05:04,120
Maybe after you get a job.

717
01:05:05,880 --> 01:05:09,400
Maybe after you get
to live the life you want.

718
01:05:11,760 --> 01:05:15,120
When you’re ready,
I’m gonna propose to you.

719
01:05:20,320 --> 01:05:22,360
I might not be ready
for the rest of my life.

720
01:05:26,520 --> 01:05:30,080
I’m ready to take care
of you for the rest of my life.

721
01:05:42,040 --> 01:05:43,440
Then please wait for me.

722
01:05:51,880 --> 01:05:55,520
Hey! Hey! Hey! Hey!
We’re outdoors now.

723
01:05:55,520 --> 01:05:57,680
Didn’t know you were a PDA couple.

724
01:05:57,720 --> 01:06:00,080
Hey, P' Payu! Let me down!

725
01:06:00,800 --> 01:06:03,040
- Let me down!
